<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        aṟattoṭu niṉṟapiṉ vēṇṭuvaṉa tarutaṟkup pirinta talaimakaṉ varaivoṭuvantuḻi muṉpu talaimakaḷ nutaṟkaṭ pacuppunīṅkumvaṇṇam tōṉṟiya katirppukkāṭṭic cevilikkut tōḻi colliyatu.  </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">
        After having stood with the truth, spoken by the confidante to the foster mother, showing the brightness [of] the colour of palour leaving in the forehead of the heroine, [right] before when the hero who had separated in order to give the things that were desired, came with a marriage [proposal], 
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink105">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻi vēṇ ṭaṉṉai muḻaṅkukaṭaṟ</l>
<l>ṟiraitaru muttam veṇmaṇa limaikkun</l>
<l>ṟaṇṇan tuṟaivaṉ vanteṉap</l>
<l>poṉṉiṉuñ civantaṉṟu kaṇṭici ṉutalē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother,</l>
<l>Because the man of the cool harbour</l>
<l>In which pearls that are given by the waves</l>
<l>Of the roaring ocean glitter upon the white sand came,</l>
<l>If you look, [her] forehead has reddened even more than gold.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
